desc: A Dose Of Honey Skincare Products & Co.

layout.text: Here at A Dose Of Honey Skincare Products & Company we promote health over wealth to our people. We provide strictly vegan and all-natural skincare four our people, made by our people. We also promote self love. At ADOH we believe that everyone should be happy in their own skin and that our scars are what makes us beautiful. Here we believe wholeheartedly that self love is the best love.
